455
0:18:22.26,000 --> 0:18:24,000
I mean, can you picture

456
0:18:24.26,000 --> 0:18:27,000
a politician standing up in Britain and saying,

457
0:18:27.26,000 --> 0:18:3,000
"GDP fell two percent this year. Good news!

458
0:18:30.26,000 --> 0:18:32,000
